phrases: I barely had any chances to speak to Onodera,
and then I got locked inside the storehouse with Kirisaki.
Anyways, the issue at hand is that we were seen by Onodera!
There is no use in wallowing in depression, all right?
I just do not have it in me to go after a boy who already has a girlfriend.
It feels like it is something that you just do not do.
Well, not that you have done anything yet.
What are you going to do now?
Wait, you still have that key?
I think she said it was the key to a bookcase in her house, or something.
Or do you actually intend to look for the boy you made that promise with ten years ago?
In that case, I will be glad to create an opportunity for you to find out how he feels.
It just so happens that I need to ask Kirisaki-san for a favor, anyway.
What are you going to do?
I am getting a bad feeling about this...
There is no question that Ichijou-kun has a crush on Kosaki.
Although it is just a woman's intuition.
Frankly, those two have been acting suspicious, too!
You see, our swim team is pretty weak.
We have got a practice meet tomorrow, but we are a bit short on members.
I have no doubt that you are athletic enough.
If you do not mind, I would really like you to join us.
Oh, that is totally fine with me!
Miyamoto, is not this the girls' swim team?
Because I have a favor to ask of you too.
Well, we will get into that later.
I cannot get over that conversation about the promise!
I am not in any shape to help.
Why did you register me as a swimmer...
when I cannot swim at all?
There is no way I will be of any help!
Oh my god, Onodera is as cute in a swimsuit as I imagined!
It is the same one that she dropped the other day!
All I heard was that Kirisaki-san would be coming.
Onodera did say it was the key to a bookcase,
but if that is all it is, there is no way she would carry it 24/7!
Do not tell me... that key's actually...
What am I supposed to do?
What the hell do you think you are doing?
There is no way that Ichijou-kun could possibly have feelings for me.
And now Kirisaki-san is here with us too.
How am I supposed to act?
Also, this feels a little awkward...
By the way, what were you two up to inside that storehouse yesterday?
In the darkness” of a sealed room,” just the two of you,”
Th-That was a prank my guys played on us.
We kind of lost our balance.
You guys were actually doing something indecent, were not you?
I hear that Kirisaki-san and Onodera are going to help out the girls' swim team!
What a magnificent sight you are!
Ichijou-kun, about that favor I need from you...
I want you to teach Kosaki how to swim by tomorrow's meet.
Today we are going to teach you how to swim.
I am your other instructor, Kirisaki Chitoge!
Looking forward to working with you!
I never dreamed this would ever happen!
I am getting a little nervous!
I guess Ichijou-kun is teaching me how to swim.
I am getting a little nervous.
Hey, Onodera, so you really cannot swim?
She set this up without asking me.
But I wonder why she is making you help out when she knows you cannot swim.
Um... I am really sorry, Kirisaki-san, for making you do this on such short notice.
Just leave all the hard work to me and forget everything else!
I can see why Ichijou-kun picked you.
You are such a lovely person, Kirisaki-san.
We may be indoors, but if you have got a swimsuit on, that means sunblock!
Shall I rub it on for you?
If you are going to get in the way, would you mind going home?
Oh, c'mon, Ruri-chan, you are such a spoilsport!
You can pay me when you are rich!
Wait a sec, where is Four Eyes?
Is not he staking us out today?
I mean, Shuu could have gotten himself shot just now.
Your Claude could not be happier!
I am going to start by showing you how it is done, so watch closely.
Did you get the general idea?
I tried so hard to help her... so why?
A-Anyway, you cannot swim at all, right, Onodera?
Let us start with the basics of the basics!
All right, why do not we start off easy with some leg kicks?
Wow, one-on-one swimming lessons with Onodera?
This was totally unthinkable until now.
Her cleavage is showing a little thanks to her swimsuit being a little damp!
Hold on, I am totally holding hands with her like it is the most natural thing in the world!
Onodera's hands... so soft and warm...
M-Make sure you do not let go, okay?
No, it is my fault for not being able to swim.
No, it was all my fault.
What do you want to do now?
No, no, you are taking the time to teach me.
I am going to go buy some drinks.
It would be wrong not to show my gratitude.
Now I am pumped up to make sure Onodera learns how to swim!
If this turns out to be... that key from ten years ago...
then Onodera's... the girl I made that promise with.
But... if there was ever a time to find out...
The key will not go in!
Was the head shaped like this?
I got you some tea, Ichijou-kun!
How dare you make a girl run your errands!
What are you planning to do with the key to the girls' locker room?
I knew you were a bean sprout...
but who knew you were such a perverted bean sprout?
It is not what it looks like!
It is not what you think!
That is what they all say!
Come on, let us go, Onodera-san.
Do not look at me like that!
I had no idea what that key was for!
Who designs a locker room key like that in the first place?
Oh, well, for some reason, they decided to go retro for the girls' locker room key.
Although, I hear it is just the principal's personal taste.
Ichijou-kun is saying that it is a misunderstanding.
Plus, I do not really see him as the type to peep on girls.
You would better be grateful to Kosaki!
But in return, you are going to see to it that Kosaki learns to swim by tomorrow, no matter what!
Because I am letting you off the hook just this once.
Oh, no, do not mention it.
Hey, sorry about this, Kirisaki-san, but I am borrowing your boyfriend.
It is not like it is the end of the world for me!
What was that pause just now?
Could it be that... my hunch was right all along?
The Day of the Practice Meet
After all that, one day was not long enough for her to learn how to swim.
We practiced all evening long after school ended.
Hey, where do the athletes sign in?
So even you are not audacious enough to wear a bikini today, huh?
I did not have a choice yesterday!
It was on short notice, and I had not bought a school swimsuit yet.
Could it be that you wanted to see me in my bikini, Darling?
Seriously, if only you were not a gorilla inside, you would be perfect.
How far did you get with Onodera-san?
If she uses a kickboard, she can barely manage.
Then that means she has not learned to swim!
How can you expect anyone to learn to swim in a single day?
As a matter of fact, I think I deserve some praise!
Sure, she might need kickboard, but she can swim 25 meters now!
I do not want to hear any whining coming from a boy.
If you take on a job, then finish it!
Is not that what a real man would do?
Right where it hurts the most...
I imagined myself swimming last night in the bathtub, too!
All you need to do is somehow finish the race.
I am going to do my best!
Why do you act so differently with her than when you are with me?
Why should I have to be nice to someone like you?
I could say the same about you!
All I am saying is that seeing this blatant difference in treatment pisses me off!
Yeah, well, you treat Onodera and me differently, too!
Now you are asking for way too much, buddy!
I am a lady, you know!
You are supposed to treat me like a princess!
I did not know someone who is a gorilla on the inside counted as a lady too!
Are they fighting because they are close?
Or is it because they cannot stand each other?
If I had to guess, I would pick the latter.
But it is so different from their usual routine
that I just cannot get a handle on what they really think about each other.
Would it kill you to warm up a little?
It is going to be fine.
After all, I practiced so much yesterday.
Holy crap, she does not know the first thing about being a sweet girl!
One day was not enough for her to master swimming.
As long as she does not end up drowning or anything.
But Kosaki has always been unbelievably slow to learn anything, so...
This pool's shallow enough for her to stand in.
So there is no way that she would...
Does that girl look like she is drowning?
Would it kill you to warm up a little?
I will go get a teacher!
I do not think she swallowed too much water.
That is not something you leave to an amateur!
Who else can we count on?
I mean, come on, right in public, too?
Not to mention in front of Onodera!
No, this is an emergency, and every second counts!
Wait, am I an idiot or something?
This is no time to hesitate!
If I do not do this now, I am not a real man, am I?
What do you think you are doing?
Ichijou-kun was something else, was not he?
Rescuing Kirisaki-san in such a dashing manner.
Do you wish you were the one drowning instead?
N-No, that thought never crossed my mind!
Well, I admit that he does not seem to be just another loser.
At the end of the day, are those two on good terms or bad?
Their chemistry seems good and bad at the same time.
This gets more confusing by the second, huh?
The one thing I am sure of now, though, is that they do not seem to actually be dating.
Wow, you brought that key with you?
I cannot believe you would hold onto a trinket from someone you met ten years ago so faithfully.
Well, it is precious to me.
Yeah, but all you remember about that boy is that he had a pendant with a keyhole, right?
To think that you do not remember anything else...
If you ask me, just hoping for a reunion with someone like that is a waste of time.
Is not the love that you have here and now more important?
That love from ten years ago just might be connected to my current love...
Ichijou-kun might have mistakenly thought that that locker room key was this key, you know?
Onodera and the others sure are late.
Got To hand it to the girls' swim team!
Do not play dumb with me!
I am talking about Onodera and Kirisaki-san's bodies!
I got to say, I think I am in the Onodera camp.
I mean, Kirisaki-san's breasts are the bomb,
but she is also a bit fleshy, you could say?
Not that I do not go for that, too...
But hey, which do you prefer?
I made Valentine's Day chocolates for you all!
Do not you think this chocolate's a little too bitter
It is too hard to chew
I have always thought your chocolates are the best, year after year!
Hey, Raku, did you get any Valentine's Day chocolates?
I am about to get a boatload of them.
Well, how do you like this year's chocolates?
I think this year's turned out well, if I do say so myself.
I never did manage to give Ichijou-kun my Valentine's Day chocolates.
Are you giving them to someone?
You are not giving them to anyone?
Hey, these are pretty good for homemade chocolates!
She is foaming at the mouth!
Kirisaki has been invited to celebrate the New Year at the Ichijou home.
We would appreciate it if you would show us your specialty!
Well, guess I have no choice!
Would rather love than be loved.
If that is the code of this household...
Do not ever show the enemy your back!
That is the way of a just man.
